  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosed with Multiple Sclerosis,classified as relapsing remitting,or
             primary/secondary progressive

          -  Expanded Disability Status Scale (EDSS)score of ≤ 6

          -  Reduced walking ability (subjectively experienced)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  persons with a level of ataxia, clinically assessed, that would affect their ability
             to perform the training.

          -  spasticity requiring stretching og treatment with baclofen.

          -  Other, not MS-related, conditions affecting walking ability.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
